#### 4. `EntityCache` — 废弃，委托给新 Manager

```java
@Component
@RequiredArgsConstructor
@Deprecated  // 迁移完成后删除，预计 Sprint N+2
public class EntityCache {

    private static final String LEGACY_TENANT = "__default__";

    private final TenantEntityCacheManager cacheManager;

    @Deprecated
    public void cacheEntityId(String key, Long entityId, int ttl) {
        cacheManager.cacheEntityId(LEGACY_TENANT, stripPrefix(key), entityId, ttl);
    }

    @Deprecated
    public Long getCachedEntityId(String key) {
        return cacheManager.getCachedEntityId(LEGACY_TENANT, stripPrefix(key));
    }

    // 剥离旧 prefix "entity:exist:" 以适配新 namespaced() 逻辑
    private String stripPrefix(String key) {
        return key.startsWith("entity:exist:") ? key.substring("entity:exist:".length()) : key;
    }
}
```

